      "title": "Crude oil prices down",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The price of a barrel of crude oil in the world crude oil market has seen a drop today (01).",
        "Accordingly, the price of a barrel of WTI crude oil was recorded as 97.47 US dollars and the price of a barrel of Brent crude oil was recorded as 103.1 US dollars."
      ],
